    DISC2ARPAbet

    DISC2HTK
    Translates CELEX-DISC-encoded transcriptions like tr{nskrIpS@n to a form that would word for a Hidden Markov Model Toolkit (HTK) .dict file, like: t r _{ n s k r I p S _@ n.
    DISC2IPA

    DISC2XSAMPA
